elements.name: Verify Single and and Multiple Checkbox Field functionality

steps.name: User Navigate to SeleniumEasy Test Home Page
User Click on Input Forms hyperlink tab
User Click on Checkbox Demo linkText tab
User select Single Checkbox Demo radio button
User click on the Check All button in Multiple Checkbox Demo section
User validate the Check All message changed to Uncheck All button

name: As a user I should be able to verify the  CheckBox Demo field functionalities in Checkbox Demo Page

elements.name: Verify Single and Double Input Field Functionalities

steps.name: User Navigate to SeleniumEasy Test Home Page
User Click on Input Forms hyperlink tab
User Click on  Simple form Demo Hyperlink Test
User Enter a message in the Enter message text box
User Click on Show Message Button
User Validate the Message is been displayed in the Your Message section
User Enter a integer value in the Enter a text box
User Enter 2nd integer value in the Enter b text box
